  "detailed_description": "<h1>Version Update Plan</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/ba3a6e7e43b9a8505987f99b3aa6644c.avif?t=1727409128\" width=600 height=2132 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >60+ Unique Campaign Levels with Various Strategies</h2>The game features over 60 meticulously designed campaign levels, each presenting new buildings, new units, and different battle scenarios. How will you choose your strategy? Each level has a unique way to complete it—just capture all the castles and let your creativity flow!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/0c65f61c6fc86eddeb1c41f30d8a62f1.poster.avif?t=1727409128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/0c65f61c6fc86eddeb1c41f30d8a62f1.webm?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/0c65f61c6fc86eddeb1c41f30d8a62f1.mp4?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock New Buildings and Units, Diverse Strategic Combinations</h2>As you progress through the campaign, new buildings and units will be unlocked. The game includes 13 types of buildings and 6 distinctive units. Adapt your strategy to the different terrains and units provided at each level for a variety of tactical approaches.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/1a348cdeeb610d53ca2fc1dead2c4a4f.poster.avif?t=1727409128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/1a348cdeeb610d53ca2fc1dead2c4a4f.webm?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/1a348cdeeb610d53ca2fc1dead2c4a4f.mp4?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >100+ Player-Customized Maps, Create Your Own Maps</h2>The game offers a map editor system where you can play over 100 creative maps designed by other players. Save, comment on, or share your favorite maps. You can also edit your own map levels and upload them to share with other players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/ec9637e267d5ecf7f1f5c624b3652d24.poster.avif?t=1727409128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/ec9637e267d5ecf7f1f5c624b3652d24.webm?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/ec9637e267d5ecf7f1f5c624b3652d24.mp4?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >60+ Unique Campaign Levels with Various Strategies</h2>The game features over 60 meticulously designed campaign levels, each presenting new buildings, new units, and different battle scenarios. How will you choose your strategy? Each level has a unique way to complete it—just capture all the castles and let your creativity flow!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/0c65f61c6fc86eddeb1c41f30d8a62f1.poster.avif?t=1727409128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/0c65f61c6fc86eddeb1c41f30d8a62f1.webm?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/0c65f61c6fc86eddeb1c41f30d8a62f1.mp4?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock New Buildings and Units, Diverse Strategic Combinations</h2>As you progress through the campaign, new buildings and units will be unlocked. The game includes 13 types of buildings and 6 distinctive units. Adapt your strategy to the different terrains and units provided at each level for a variety of tactical approaches.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/1a348cdeeb610d53ca2fc1dead2c4a4f.poster.avif?t=1727409128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/1a348cdeeb610d53ca2fc1dead2c4a4f.webm?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/1a348cdeeb610d53ca2fc1dead2c4a4f.mp4?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >100+ Player-Customized Maps, Create Your Own Maps</h2>The game offers a map editor system where you can play over 100 creative maps designed by other players. Save, comment on, or share your favorite maps. You can also edit your own map levels and upload them to share with other players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/ec9637e267d5ecf7f1f5c624b3652d24.poster.avif?t=1727409128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/ec9637e267d5ecf7f1f5c624b3652d24.webm?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569410/extras/ec9637e267d5ecf7f1f5c624b3652d24.mp4?t=1727409128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
